
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Verification</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .card {
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }

        .btn-success {
            background-color: #3498db;
            border-color: #3498db;
        }

            .btn-success:hover {
                background-color: #2980b9;
                border-color: #2980b9;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card text-center" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px;">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h2>Welcome to KNFs Magazine!</h2>
            <p>Thank you for joining our community. We are delighted to have you as part of our team.</p>
            <p>Your account has been created with the following details:</p>
            <p>Please follow the link below to verify your email address and proceed with your next tasks:</p>
            <a asp-action="VerifyAccount" class="btn btn-success">Verify Email</a>
            <p class="mt-3">This link will expire in 5 minutes for your security.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact us at support@knfs-magazine.com.</p>
            <p>Thank you and have a great day!</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
